Chew[bot]ca. The un-tamed, in your face and at your side copilot to your development dreams.

Included is lib/chewy.example.rb, which you will want to tweak to your own settings.

Thanks to: matzbot, for inspiration, and Jabber::Bot . 

New: EventMachine based DCC connections. This will allow in-IRC pasting into pasties, as well as full cheatsheets. As of the current precise moment, pastie command works but not for a long period of time. Also, it is stuck to localhost right now. You can easily switch that by sending #{@host_ip.to_i} in the PRIVMSG in Chewy::Bot::dcc